### INTRO ###

This is a preprocessor for shell scripts (or other text files) and a make replacement  written for posix shells.
The make replacement is simple written and most parts can used withozut it, in any posix compilant shell (see sh_make/tools/simple_sh_make as example).


## DEPENCIES ##

 - posix compilant /bin/sh
 - posix compilant: sed, grep, sort, cat, basename, dirname and cut

## BUILD AND INSTALL ## 

See INSTALL.


## NOT WORKING/ NOT FULLY WORKING ##

Legacy mode for for files with sh_make 1.x syntax in shpp 	(not tested)



